<p>*Up to 60 minutes with a GP included with Be.Reassured and Be.Ahead.</p>
<p>Must be aged 18 years and above. Excludes all company paid schemes. 10% discount only applies to the following Bupa Health and Wellbeing plans on a self-pay basis only: Be.Motivated, Be.Reassured and Be.Ahead. Appointments are subject to availability and separate Terms and Conditions shall apply. </p>
